WEBVTT

00:03.600 --> 00:05.120
Uncle Qiu wrote saying

00:05.120 --> 00:06.600
He took a ninth concubine

00:07.040 --> 00:09.360
I sent someone with a pair of gold bracelets

00:09.480 --> 00:10.480
To tell him

00:10.480 --> 00:11.400
That's enough

00:11.480 --> 00:13.280
An eighteen-year-old bride, an eighty-year-old groom

00:13.800 --> 00:15.600
He lives more freely than I

00:16.920 --> 00:18.920
I just come here to escape the noise

00:19.160 --> 00:20.360
Don't have to listen to their nagging

00:23.040 --> 00:25.400
Fortunately, I gave birth to a daughter

00:25.480 --> 00:27.600
Can peacefully accompany Your Majesty and Yu'er

00:28.160 --> 00:30.040
Don't need to worry about other matters

00:30.600 --> 00:31.680
But Your Majesty

00:32.040 --> 00:33.920
You always bring official documents here

00:34.800 --> 00:36.040
My place here

00:36.160 --> 00:37.600
Isn't the Imperial Administration Palace
